title: Tim Mahoney
added: After news of his extramarital affair was revealed, Mahoney's wife filed for divorce on October 20, 2008, less than a month before Mahoney lost reelection to Congress. The divorce was finalized in 2010, with Mahoney and his wife splitting $2.83 million in assets, and Mahoney keeping their property in the PGA National Resort and Spa, which he used as his residence while in Congress, with his wife keeping their property in Oklahoma.<ref name="finalized">{{cite news |last1=Turner |first1=Jim |title=Mahoney divorce is now final |url=http://archive.tcpalm.com/news/mahoney-divorce-is-now-final-ep-395535391-346884682.html |access-date=February 3, 2021 |work=[[Treasure Coast Newspapers]] |date=January 14, 2010}}</ref>
